{
  "stem": "19895.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 110.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they did say that the Jewish chiefs, the [NON-ENGLISH], and these two gentlemen, out of whom I have to mention the name of Kertesz, Mr.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Kertesz, who came to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I said to him, Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Kertesz, I'm not going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he says, they are going to kill you right on the spot here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anybody who stays behind will be executed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Kertesz, I will try to hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he says, it's your choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You have a better chance of surviving if you come along with the other people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I said, I don't have the will.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't have the strength.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I have only one hope that I can hide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was a decision which just dawned upon me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I stuck to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was very nice to me at that moment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the last minute, he reached into his pouch, give me a portion of a loaf of a bread, and he said, well, try to survive on it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's the last time I saw him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They left and I was staying back with a few number of people in different barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because as we looked around and we saw some person there, some miserable sight, and that person there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in our own barrack, maybe three or four people stayed behind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Their legs were frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were sick, they were just on the verge of death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they were exhausted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was hiding behind some of the barracks structure building up here a little higher and stayed behind.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that day went by.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I heard from the distance some people moaning and shouting and then silence and gunshots.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was pretty sure that that's execution.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
